{"tid":2223759,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"悼周梓樂期間遺雷射筆 文員涉藏攻擊性武器提堂","createTime":"2020-09-30T05:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T05:22:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4a7c3faadee3b6574eb635a66819bd612412ec","tid":2223759,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"科大學生周梓樂逝世4個月時，有市民分別於將軍澳及觀塘舉行悼念活動。大批防暴警員到達將軍澳尚德停車場一帶驅趕市民，現場一名文員奔跑期間疑遺下雷射筆，遭警員拘捕。文員被控一項《公安條例》下在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，案件今於觀塘裁判法院提堂。被告獲准保釋候訊，惟其間須宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/6HITTVFYTND7RKNPLZIURORW5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2F6HITTVFYTND7RKNPLZIURORW5A%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWMfSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=15146ecc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2F6HITTVFYTND7RKNPLZIURORW5A%2F&h=e7eb62f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/6HITTVFYTND7RKNPLZIURORW5A/</a>"}]}